### Get Student dashboard stats (Requires STUDENT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Get Student lessons (Requires STUDENT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/lessons
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Get Student progress history (Requires STUDENT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/progress
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Get Student skills breakdown (Requires STUDENT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/skills
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Get Student achievements (Requires STUDENT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/achievements
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Mark Student achievement notifications as seen (Requires STUDENT)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/achievements/notifications/seen
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Mark Student achievement notifications as seen - 403 (wrong role)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/achievements/notifications/seen
Authorization: Bearer {{teacher_token}}

### Get detailed result of completed lesson (Requires STUDENT)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/lessons/1/result
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Get detailed result of completed lesson — 404 LESSON_NOT_FOUND
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/lessons/999999/result
Authorization: Bearer {{student_token}}

### Get detailed result of completed lesson — 401 (no token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/student/lessons/1/result
